<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1036481' id='t-1036481'>how they measure their progress
toward those dreams,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1038974' id='t-1038974'>and what resources they need
to make them come true,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1041633' id='t-1041633'>regardless of what the overhead is.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1043420' id='t-1043420'>Who cares what the overhead is</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1045048' id='t-1045048'>if these problems
are actually getting solved?</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
17:39
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1048367' id='t-1048367'>If we can have that kind of generosity --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1051367' id='t-1051367'>a generosity of thought --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1053519' id='t-1053519'>then the non-profit sector
can play a massive role</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1056419' id='t-1056419'>in changing the world
for all those citizens</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1059875' id='t-1059875'>most desperately in need of it to change.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1065816' id='t-1065816'>And if that can be
our generation's enduring legacy --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1070662' id='t-1070662'>that we took responsibility</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1073558' id='t-1073558'>for the thinking that had
